                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9621" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1448</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1600 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股票回购借风起，“忽悠”梦醒跌深渊 ——合纵科技回购“爽约”的财务真实性陷阱</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Stock buybacks are on the rise, &quot;fooling&quot; people out of their dreams and plunging into the abyss——The financial authenticity trap of Hezong Technology&#39;s &quot;missed appointment&quot; in share repurchase</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鲁美娟，张琳琳，魏文静，纪冰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京合纵科技有限责任公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“忽悠式”回购；股票回购；政策风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot; scam style&quot; repurchase;share buybacks; Policy risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023年证监会发布的《上市公司股票回购规则》进一步规范上市公司回购行为的同时加大了对“忽悠式”股票回购的打击力度。股票回购作为企业市值管理、回报股东的重要方式受到众多上市公司的欢迎，但存在一些上市公司进行“忽悠式”股票回购欺骗投资者及其他利益相关者。本案例选取因“一股未购”而被各大媒体重点报道的合纵科技股票回购因信息披露质量违规被北京证监局责令改正的处罚事件，结合行业背景，描述股票回购历程，通过企业股票回购公告前后的财务数据对比揭示企业进行“忽悠式”股票回购的动因及后果。引导学员通过分析公司财务数据真实性陷阱识别“忽悠式”股票回购风险，并进一步引发学员关于如何防范“忽悠式”股票回购的风险及加强对上市公司对“忽悠式”股票回购监管的思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2023,the China Securities Regulatory Commission (CSRC) issued the Rules for Share Repurchase of Listed Companies,which further regulates the repurchase behavior of listed companies and intensifies the crackdown on &quot;scam style&quot; repurchase.As an important way to manage the market value of enterprises and return shareholders,share repurchase is welcomed by many listed companies,but there are some listed companies that carry out&quot;scam style&quot;repurchase to deceive investors and other stakeholders.In this case,we select the stock repurchase event of Hezong Technology,which has been highlighted by major media,and describes the stock repurchase process in combination with the industry background,and analyzes the motivation and consequences of the company&#39;s&quot;scam style&quot;repurchase through the comparison of data before and after the company&#39;s stock repurchase announcement. Guide the trainees to identify the risks of &quot;deceptive&quot; stock repurchases by analyzing the authenticity traps in the company&#39;s financial data, and further stimulate their thinking on how to prevent the risks of &quot;deceptive&quot; stock repurchases and strengthen the supervision of listed companies over such repurchases.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自由现金流假说；内部控制理论；信号传递理论；管理者机会主义假说；再融资风险：财务风险；信誉风险；政策风险；</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
